---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '@rodrigopsasaki/config';
---

<BaseLayout title="Início">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-50 dark:bg-monokai-bg">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in">
        <!-- Greeting with animated typing effect -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {siteConfig.availableForWork && (
            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-monokai-surface text-primary-700 dark:text-monokai-green rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 dark:bg-monokai-green rounded-full mr-2 animate-pulse"></span>
              Disponível para novas oportunidades
            </div>
          )}
          
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text mb-4">
            Oi, eu sou <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-monokai-yellow">Rodrigo</span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-monokai-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Eu construo sistemas de software bem pensados que priorizam clareza, manutenibilidade e experiência do desenvolvedor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Action Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-8">
          <a href="/pt-BR/blog" 
             class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary-600 dark:bg-monokai-orange text-white font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
            <span>Ler Blog</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/pt-BR/projects" 
             class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-monokai-surface text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text font-semibold rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-monokai-border hover:bg-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-monokai-border transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
            <span>Ver Projetos</span>
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-monokai-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text mb-4">
          Sobre mim
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-monokai-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Me importo com arquitetura limpa, realidade de produção e com o engenheiro que recebe uma chamada às 2 da manhã e precisa resolver problemas no sistema que ajudei a construir.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group p-8 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-monokai-surface rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-300 dark:border-monokai-border hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 dark:bg-monokai-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text mb-3">Clareza Antes de Esperteza</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-monokai-muted">
            Me esforço para escrever código que é entediante da melhor forma — claro, previsível e honesto. Algo que meu eu futuro (ou outra pessoa) possa entender e confiar.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-monokai-surface rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-300 dark:border-monokai-border hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-600 dark:bg-monokai-purple rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text mb-3">Simplicidade</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-monokai-muted">
            Me importo com simplicidade que se mantém sob pressão. Bons padrões. Contratos claros. Código que convida ao entendimento, não à explicação.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-monokai-surface rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-300 dark:border-monokai-border hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-700 dark:bg-monokai-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-monokai-text mb-3">Pensamento Production-First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-monokai-muted">
            Projeto sistemas para o mundo real — onde logs importam, falhas acontecem e alguém está sempre de plantão. Construo com observabilidade, resiliência e clareza desde o início.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Recent Work Preview -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-monokai-bg">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
          Trabalhos e pensamentos recentes
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="group p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50 dark:from-primary-950/20 dark:to-accent-950/20 rounded-2xl border border-primary-200/50 dark:border-primary-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Posts do Blog</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
            Mergulhos profundos em arquitetura e experiência do desenvolvedor. Ou alguns pensamentos aleatórios.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
            Insights técnicos, lições aprendidas e opiniões sobre construir software melhor.
          </p>
          <a href="/pt-BR/blog" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">
            Ler mais
            <svg class="ml-1 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-primary-50 dark:from-accent-950/20 dark:to-primary-950/20 rounded-2xl border border-accent-200/50 dark:border-accent-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Projetos</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
            Projetos open source e ferramentas que desenvolvi
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
            De ferramentas para desenvolvedores a aplicações web, explore o que tenho construído.
          </p>
          <a href="/pt-BR/projects" class="inline-flex items-center text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 font-medium group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">
            Explorar projetos
            <svg class="ml-1 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>